Change "changeme" to the OCP cluster name and fill the requested variables; vars/vars-create-changeme-from-acm.yml

ocp_cluster variable should be provided as extra variable and the value should be OCP cluster name.

ACM OCP credential and Vcenter credentails should be provided as AAP Credentails

#Sample Workflows#

To Create a new cluster;

main-create-vms.yml  >> main-create-cluster.yml >> main-initialize-cluster.yml

To Scale out an existing Cluster;

main-create-cluster.yml >> main-scale-cluster.yml


